===Noun===
'''[[food]] [[chain]]'''
# The [[feeding]] [[relationship]]s between [[species]] in a [[biotic]] [[community]].

===Usage notes===
Because the concept of the '''food chain''' implies a feeding [[hierarchy]] proceding upwards to a top [[predator]], modern [[ecologist]]s usually prefer the term [[food web]], since that term allows for a more complicated system of interactions.

